'''Forak''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Trandosha/Legends|Trandosha]]. In downtown Forak, there was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] repair center located on [[Banir Avenue]].

[[Trandoshan/Legends|Trandoshan]] [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenary]] and [[Assassin/Legends|assassin]] [[Nakaron]] was exiled from Forak after showing anti-social behavior towards the city's Elders.

